note right of RunnableSequence
  Built with the pipe operator:
  prompt | model | parser
  Every step must be a Runnable.
end note

note right of RunnableWithMessageHistory
  Uses BaseChatMessageHistory to
  inject and persist per-session
  messages around any Runnable.
  Alternative to LangGraph memory
  for simpler LCEL chains.
end note

